 y6d ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Africa-Indian Ocean Division. </div><div class="t m78 x1f hb y6e ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Bread of Life—</div><div class="t m79 x1f hb y6f ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Living Water—</div><div class="t m7a x1f hb y70 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">You can give these gifts of eternal life to the </div><div class="t m7b x1f hb y71 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spiritually starving. </div><div class="t m7c x1f h10 y63 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SPIRITUAL STARVATION—</div><div class="t m7d x1f h10 y72 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">You can help stop it. </div><div class="t m7e x1f h10 y73 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Thirteenth Sabbath Offering </div><div class="t m7f x20 h10 y74 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">September 28 </div><div class="t m80 x21 h11 y75 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">My</div><div class="t m81 x22 h11 y75 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.</div><div class="t m82 x23 h11 y75 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Personal </div><div class="t m83 x24 h11 y76 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Giving Plan </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
